            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Marti et Victo<lb break="no" n="2"/>riae <lb n="3"/>Soemus Severus <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>cornicul</abbr><ex>arius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> &amp;lt;I=T&amp;gt; <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>aviae</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Damas</abbr><ex>cenorum</ex></expan> |(milliariae) <expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>uitatae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>sag</abbr><ex>ittariorum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Autopsie R. Wiegels. Z. 4: hinter COH T statt I mit überstrichener Querhaste.</p>
